WEBVTT

00:00:00.980 --> 00:00:04.430
July 15th (Thurs)  8:30 PM

00:00:06.270 --> 00:00:08.380
This isn't good... This isn't good at all!

00:00:08.380 --> 00:00:10.710
I need to let Yoshikage know!

00:00:11.340 --> 00:00:12.550
Reimi!

00:00:12.550 --> 00:00:15.110
You took this picture, Rohan?

00:00:15.490 --> 00:00:16.810
Yes, why?

00:00:16.810 --> 00:00:20.200
This one is marked. Is there 
something wrong with it?

00:00:20.200 --> 00:00:23.080
The one you have circled looks a little boy.

00:00:20.220 --> 00:00:23.070
Hayato Kawajiri

00:00:23.520 --> 00:00:25.710
Oh, him...

00:00:25.710 --> 00:00:27.730
It's nothing, really.

00:00:27.730 --> 00:00:31.210
He seemed to be snooping around, 
so he caught my attention.

00:00:31.750 --> 00:00:37.470
But this boy, Hayato Kawajiri, has the 
same last name as this man here.

00:00:38.040 --> 00:00:39.570
Huh? Really?

00:00:39.570 --> 00:00:40.470
Look!

00:00:40.490 --> 00:00:41.260
Kosaku Kawajiri

00:00:40.920 --> 00:00:42.180
It's the same.

00:00:42.180 --> 00:00:43.980
You're the one who 
researched this, aren't you?

00:00:45.450 --> 00:00:47.290
They do have the same last name.

00:00:49.250 --> 00:00:54.270
At this rate, Rohan Kishibe will 
find his way to Yoshikage!

00:00:53.630 --> 00:00:55.940
July 15th (Thurs)  8:48 PM

00:00:57.990 --> 00:01:00.740
Hayato? Hayato!

00:01:01.300 --> 00:01:02.400
Ugh...

00:01:03.420 --> 00:01:05.440
Hayato, I've been calling you!

00:01:05.440 --> 00:01:07.180
You can at least answer me!

00:01:10.700 --> 00:01:12.130
D-Darling...

00:01:12.680 --> 00:01:16.470
I thought it was Hayato in the bath.

00:01:16.470 --> 00:01:19.170
I mean, look at this!

00:01:19.170 --> 00:01:22.910
Hayato left his clothes in the hallway 
as if they exploded off of him.

00:01:22.910 --> 00:01:26.350
Unlike you, no matter how many 
times I warn him, he's such a slob.

00:01:26.350 --> 00:01:28.860
And he's not answering me again.

00:01:28.860 --> 00:01:32.980
I'm sure he's probably got his 
headphones on, reading manga again.

00:01:33.510 --> 00:01:37.200
Oh! Darling, your fingers are bleeding.

00:01:37.200 --> 00:01:38.660
What happened?

00:01:38.660 --> 00:01:40.720
We need to put a bandage on it.

00:01:43.070 --> 00:01:45.620
I-I'll do it myself.

00:01:46.410 --> 00:01:49.880
I can apply a bandage myself.

00:01:49.880 --> 00:01:50.880
Okay...

00:01:53.100 --> 00:01:56.380
I just got my fingers caught 
in the door, that's all.

00:02:17.400 --> 00:02:18.650
Jojo's Bizarre Adventure

00:02:17.400 --> 00:02:18.650
Diamond is Unbreakable

00:03:25.990 --> 00:03:29.130
July 15th (Thurs)  8:50 PM

00:03:28.750 --> 00:03:30.230
Hayato Kawajiri?

00:03:30.640 --> 00:03:33.790
Are you saying this grade-schooler has 
something to do with Yoshikage Kira?

00:03:31.560 --> 00:03:37.010
Episode 35    Bites the Dust, Part 1

00:03:34.250 --> 00:03:37.330
We're not 100% sure yet,

00:03:37.330 --> 00:03:40.280
but Rohan-sensei said 
something bugs him about it.

00:03:40.680 --> 00:03:46.620
True, there's something wrong if he's 
secretly taking videos of his dad.

00:03:46.620 --> 00:03:50.810
So, tomorrow morning, 
we're thinking of meeting up

00:03:50.810 --> 00:03:53.030
and going to visit Hayato Kawajiri's house.

00:03:53.030 --> 00:03:55.900
Apparently, Rohan-sensei's 
already found the address.

00:03:56.830 --> 00:03:59.590
That bastard Rohan sure works fast.

00:03:59.590 --> 00:04:03.480
All right. I just have 
to invite Okuyasu, right?

00:04:03.480 --> 00:04:06.640
And of course, there's Jotaro, too.

00:04:06.640 --> 00:04:09.570
I'll talk to Jotaro.

00:04:09.570 --> 00:04:11.780
All right. See you tomorrow at 8:30 AM

00:04:11.780 --> 00:04:13.900
at the intersection with the Pepsi sign.

00:04:13.900 --> 00:04:14.930
Got it.

00:04:15.560 --> 00:04:19.290
8:30, huh? I'm gonna be late for school.

00:04:19.690 --> 00:04:25.000
But if we talk to this kid, 
we might find something out.

00:04:32.200 --> 00:04:33.590
Are you okay?

00:04:33.590 --> 00:04:35.730
You're acting a bit strange, darling...

00:04:35.730 --> 00:04:37.420
And you look pale.

00:04:37.730 --> 00:04:39.830
I told you, it's nothing.

00:04:39.830 --> 00:04:41.680
I caught my fingers in the door.

00:04:41.680 --> 00:04:43.380
Can you blame me for being pale?

00:04:43.830 --> 00:04:46.510
More importantly, can you make me some tea?

00:04:46.510 --> 00:04:48.550
I'll be down soon.

00:04:52.030 --> 00:04:53.360
Of course.

00:04:54.690 --> 00:04:57.810
This just came to me out of the blue,

00:04:57.810 --> 00:05:02.150
but lately, I can't help but 
think that you're immortal.

00:05:03.670 --> 00:05:05.320
I'll go make you that tea now.

00:05:17.290 --> 00:05:21.650
If something happens to me, 
your secret's going to be found out!

00:05:21.650 --> 00:05:23.380
Don't you lay a finger on me or my mom!

00:05:23.840 --> 00:05:25.450
This isn't a deal!

00:05:25.450 --> 00:05:28.630
You have to listen to me! Got it?!

00:05:30.530 --> 00:05:31.580
You're too naïve!

00:05:31.580 --> 00:05:34.880
Do you really think I would allow that?

00:05:39.380 --> 00:05:43.070
I can't believe you actually 
got rid of Hayato.

00:05:43.070 --> 00:05:45.210
What a stupid thing to do.

00:05:45.210 --> 00:05:47.700
I'm trying to think of what to do right now.

00:05:47.700 --> 00:05:50.200
It's no use thinking about it.

00:05:51.390 --> 00:05:55.110
I see you made it look like
he fell and hit his head,

00:05:55.110 --> 00:05:57.860
but the timing was unfortunate.

00:05:57.860 --> 00:06:02.350
That Rohan Kishibe has started 
investigating Hayato Kawajiri.

00:06:02.350 --> 00:06:05.930
They're still not positive 
that Kosaku Kawajiri is you,

00:06:05.930 --> 00:06:09.550
but they're coming to 
check this house tomorrow.

00:06:12.750 --> 00:06:15.450
It's a bad idea to stay in this house any longer.

00:06:15.450 --> 00:06:17.790
Shut up. I'm thinking right now.

00:06:22.770 --> 00:06:26.850
Ever since you were a child, 
when things didn't go your way

00:06:26.850 --> 00:06:30.490
and there was nothing you could do, 
you would always bite your nails.

00:06:32.120 --> 00:06:33.970
You poor thing.

00:06:33.970 --> 00:06:37.370
You must be in so much despair right now.

00:06:39.870 --> 00:06:42.030
There's no other way around it.

00:06:42.030 --> 00:06:45.130
You're going to have to 
leave this town, Yoshikage.

00:06:45.130 --> 00:06:50.290
If you go now, you can escape to someplace 
they can't follow you, before they find out.

00:06:52.430 --> 00:06:55.970
Are you telling me to flee Morioh?

00:06:55.970 --> 00:06:59.890
You know very well that I'm done 
with living my life in fear,

00:06:59.890 --> 00:07:03.860
having to worry about 
someone coming after me!

00:07:04.680 --> 00:07:07.070
I will never leave this town.

00:07:14.120 --> 00:07:15.690
What?!

00:07:16.540 --> 00:07:20.490
The arrow acted on its own! 
I didn't do anything!

00:07:20.490 --> 00:07:23.000
I didn't even touch the arrow!

00:07:24.800 --> 00:07:26.590
Th-The arrow...

00:07:29.990 --> 00:07:31.760
Y-Yoshikage!

00:07:43.350 --> 00:07:46.570
Hayato! Hayato?!

00:07:44.920 --> 00:07:46.560
July 16th (Fri)  7:30 AM

00:07:46.570 --> 00:07:49.070
Are you planning to sleep all day, Hayato?

00:07:49.750 --> 00:07:51.390
Hurry up and wake—

00:07:53.800 --> 00:07:58.580
What, you're already 
awake? That's a surprise.

00:07:58.580 --> 00:08:00.550
Hayato, breakfast is ready.

00:08:00.550 --> 00:08:02.770
Honestly, why don't you ever answer me?

00:08:07.260 --> 00:08:09.550
I couldn't sleep very well last night.

00:08:09.990 --> 00:08:14.780
He... He found out that 
I saw him kill someone.

00:08:15.400 --> 00:08:19.080
Anyway, I made sure that he 
wouldn't be able to lay a finger

00:08:19.080 --> 00:08:20.720
on me or Mom, but...

00:08:22.430 --> 00:08:24.270
What should I do now?

00:08:43.270 --> 00:08:47.790
I-I don't understand... 
What happened, Yoshikage?

00:08:49.170 --> 00:08:51.510
You've been acting strange since last night.

00:08:53.000 --> 00:08:55.060
Listen to me, Yoshikage!

00:08:55.060 --> 00:08:59.990
That Rohan Kishibe has started investigating 
Hayato Kawajiri for some reason!

00:08:59.990 --> 00:09:03.580
They're going to come 
check this house tomorrow.

00:09:04.460 --> 00:09:06.400
There's no need to worry.

00:09:06.400 --> 00:09:09.230
B-But, Yoshikage!

00:09:12.080 --> 00:09:15.830
Deadly Queen has gained a third ability.

00:09:22.660 --> 00:09:24.250
I... I don't understand.

00:09:25.190 --> 00:09:29.420
What could have happened 
to make you so carefree?

00:09:29.440 --> 00:09:31.950
-Morioh's Very Own-

00:09:29.440 --> 00:09:31.950
Miso-stewed Cow Tongue

00:09:29.690 --> 00:09:31.360
Miso-stewed cow tongue.

00:09:34.940 --> 00:09:37.770
What? No way! We're on the air already?

00:09:38.490 --> 00:09:43.720
Er, um... It's now 7:55, so here's 
the weather today for the prefecture.

00:09:44.080 --> 00:09:46.940
Today should be sunny.

00:09:46.940 --> 00:09:51.060
Hayato! Hey, Hayato! Answer the phone.

00:09:53.020 --> 00:09:57.090
After that bath last night, he changed.

00:09:57.090 --> 00:09:59.480
Wh-What could have happened?

00:10:01.700 --> 00:10:05.910
Hayato! I asked you to answer the phone!

00:10:07.980 --> 00:10:08.860
Crash

00:10:10.410 --> 00:10:12.380
My precious tea set!

00:10:13.400 --> 00:10:15.080
This is all your fault!

00:10:15.080 --> 00:10:18.260
Why do you always ignore me?!

00:10:18.260 --> 00:10:21.720
Fine! You think your mother's 
just a bother, right?!

00:10:21.720 --> 00:10:23.590
Do whatever you want, then!

00:10:24.630 --> 00:10:28.390
Now, now. Let's not fight 
first thing in the morning.

00:10:28.910 --> 00:10:31.520
If it broke, I'll just buy you another one.

00:10:32.560 --> 00:10:34.650
Hello, Kawajiri residence.

00:10:35.140 --> 00:10:36.790
No, it's not.

00:10:37.240 --> 00:10:39.660
They had the wrong number.

00:10:39.660 --> 00:10:43.670
Hayato's just at an age where 
he doesn't want to talk much.

00:10:45.340 --> 00:10:49.320
We're family, so we all need to get along.

00:10:49.320 --> 00:10:50.640
You know, get along.

00:10:51.320 --> 00:10:53.500
Well, I'll head off to work now.

00:10:54.480 --> 00:10:57.270
Do you mind if I give you a goodbye kiss?

00:10:57.270 --> 00:10:58.260
Huh?

00:10:58.700 --> 00:11:00.050
I'll be off now.

00:11:19.800 --> 00:11:21.890
H-He left...

00:11:21.890 --> 00:11:23.820
No, I'm right here.

00:11:24.990 --> 00:11:27.400
Why don't we walk together part of the way?

00:11:33.800 --> 00:11:38.090
Going from feeling refreshed 
to falling into despair...

00:11:38.090 --> 00:11:43.050
So much has happened lately. 
I've been on an emotional roller coaster.

00:11:43.590 --> 00:11:48.500
But now I'll be able to feel at ease.

00:11:48.500 --> 00:11:53.010
Since you cornered me last 
night, I was able to mature.

00:11:54.320 --> 00:11:58.800
Really, your will last night was so strong.

00:11:58.800 --> 00:12:02.230
To think that you would actually turn 
around and threaten me, Yoshikage Kira...

00:12:02.560 --> 00:12:05.620
Y-Yoshikage Kira?

00:12:07.030 --> 00:12:08.620
Did I just say my real name?

00:12:08.880 --> 00:12:11.180
A-Are you planning to kill me after all?

00:12:11.180 --> 00:12:12.380
Kill you?

00:12:12.380 --> 00:12:14.800
Because you found out my secret?

00:12:14.800 --> 00:12:18.630
There's no need for that. 
Because I've matured.

00:12:19.100 --> 00:12:21.660
No matter where you go and 
what you do with anyone,

00:12:21.660 --> 00:12:23.930
it doesn't matter, because 
now, none can rival me.

00:12:24.930 --> 00:12:29.310
I have no interest in you anymore. 
If I wanted to kill you...

00:12:30.110 --> 00:12:32.770
I would have gotten rid of you last night.

00:12:33.150 --> 00:12:36.770
From now on, we're all going to get 
along and live happily together.

00:12:36.770 --> 00:12:39.970
So just relax... Like we're family.

00:12:41.270 --> 00:12:43.490
Well, I have to head to the station.

00:12:43.490 --> 00:12:46.490
Make sure you study hard, Hayato.

00:12:50.660 --> 00:12:54.890
Rival... He just said none can rival him...

00:12:54.890 --> 00:12:57.010
Which means there must be others

00:12:57.010 --> 00:13:00.590
that have the same kind of abilities as him.

00:13:00.590 --> 00:13:03.750
But what's with that creepy confidence?

00:13:04.160 --> 00:13:08.490
If he's unrivaled now, does that mean 
he's gained some other abilities?

00:13:09.420 --> 00:13:10.730
What should I do?

00:13:12.220 --> 00:13:16.210
What am I supposed to do?

00:13:20.130 --> 00:13:21.440
You're...

00:13:21.440 --> 00:13:23.230
Hayato Kawajiri-kun,

00:13:24.990 --> 00:13:25.820
aren't you?

