Kosaku Kawajiri

00:13:32.950 --> 00:13:36.240
July 16th (Fri)  8:24 AM

00:13:33.490 --> 00:13:35.300
I've been waiting for you.

00:13:35.780 --> 00:13:37.580
My name is Rohan Kishibe.

00:13:38.090 --> 00:13:41.800
There's something that I wanted 
to ask you out of curiosity.

00:13:42.670 --> 00:13:44.440
It's about this picture.

00:13:45.420 --> 00:13:47.130
This is you, right?

00:13:48.070 --> 00:13:51.760
Were you taking video of your 
dad in the corner there?

00:13:52.620 --> 00:13:53.270
Wait.

00:13:55.100 --> 00:13:56.230
What... is this?

00:13:58.160 --> 00:14:00.190
Well, I know that was sudden...

00:14:00.190 --> 00:14:02.380
But it's much faster to just read

00:14:02.380 --> 00:14:05.870
about Hayato Kawajiri than 
to ask bothersome questions,

00:14:05.870 --> 00:14:09.160
and I can get honest answers this way, too.

00:14:09.800 --> 00:14:11.270
[Warning]

00:14:09.800 --> 00:14:11.270
You mustn't
read any further.

00:14:11.280 --> 00:14:14.240
Huh? What's that supposed to mean?

00:14:14.240 --> 00:14:16.820
What Heaven's Door turns into a book

00:14:16.820 --> 00:14:21.070
should just be the memories of this boy's 
life experiences, without any falsehoods.

00:14:21.070 --> 00:14:23.800
And yet... a warning?

00:14:22.440 --> 00:14:25.160
[Warning]
You mustn't read any further.

00:14:23.800 --> 00:14:25.170
What in the world is this?

00:14:25.170 --> 00:14:29.180
Is this "warning" what he experienced?

00:14:29.780 --> 00:14:34.280
I thought I'd just casually 
look into this child,

00:14:34.280 --> 00:14:36.930
but now this has definitely 
caught my interest.

00:14:36.930 --> 00:14:39.430
[Warning]
You mustn't read any further.

00:14:36.930 --> 00:14:39.440
"You mustn't read any further"?

00:14:39.810 --> 00:14:42.190
Who in the world could this warning be for?

00:14:46.110 --> 00:14:47.490
An old guy walked by with his fly down.

00:14:48.720 --> 00:14:50.400
He sneezed and said, "Damn it."

00:14:50.410 --> 00:14:51.810
Some women laughed at him.

00:14:51.840 --> 00:14:54.080
Wh-What is this?

00:14:54.400 --> 00:14:56.130
This is getting even more confusing.

00:14:56.130 --> 00:14:57.070
What does it mean?

00:15:00.130 --> 00:15:01.270
Damn it.

00:15:07.640 --> 00:15:10.470
J-Just who is this boy?

00:15:10.490 --> 00:15:11.750
It rained.

00:15:14.760 --> 00:15:19.050
Ugh, the forecast didn't 
say it was going to rain!

00:15:21.710 --> 00:15:23.350
At 8:27 AM, lightning struck 
above the Pepsi sign.

00:15:25.990 --> 00:15:28.190
8:27...

00:15:36.080 --> 00:15:39.200
Wh-Who in the world is this Hayato Kawajiri?

00:15:39.200 --> 00:15:41.370
Why is he experiencing things in the future?

00:15:42.380 --> 00:15:44.580
Could he be a Stand user?

00:15:48.580 --> 00:15:51.580
No... This is too odd to be a Stand ability.

00:15:51.580 --> 00:15:53.500
All I can read with Heaven's Door

00:15:53.500 --> 00:15:55.760
is what he has personally seen or heard.

00:15:55.760 --> 00:15:58.880
The answer to this should 
be written somewhere...

