My dad isn't my dad

00:16:01.300 --> 00:16:03.010
<font size="18">He made a man and a woman disappear at an apartment in Jozenji by making them explode.</c>

00:16:03.040 --> 00:16:04.510
<font size="20">He's a murderer. I found out who 
